---
import Main from '../layouts/main.astro';

---

<Main title="Horarios y edades — Ludicarte">
  <section class="prose mx-auto py-12 px-4 w-3/5 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur supports-backdrop-filter:bg-background/60">
    <h1 class="titulo__seccion">Horarios y edades</h1>
    <p>
      Aquí tienes una guía general de las actividades, sus edades recomendadas y horarios.
      <strong>¡Recibimos niños de 4 a 10 años con ganas de pasarlo bien y aprender!</strong>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pb-10">
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/60 bg-linear-to-br from-amber-50/80 via-white/70 to-rose-50/80 p-6 shadow-[0_25px_50px_-30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-white/70">
        <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-10 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-amber-200/40 blur-2xl"></div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Jornada de mañana</p>
        <p class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100/80 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900">08:00 a 13:00</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/60 bg-linear-to-br from-sky-50/80 via-white/70 to-emerald-50/80 p-6 shadow-[0_25px_50px_-30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-white/70">
        <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-10 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-emerald-200/40 blur-2xl"></div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Jornada de tarde</p>
        <p class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100/80 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">14:00 a 19:00</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Main>
